  ![antique-rustic-corrugated-metal-roof](https://www.westernstatesmetalroofing.com/hs-fs/hubfs/wsmr-gallery-page-photos/corrugated-gallery/antique-rustic-corrugated-metal-roof.jpg?width=1920&name=antique-rustic-corrugated-metal-roof.jpg)
  
  ### What Is The Price Of Corrugated Metal?
  
  ![matte black corrugated roof walls](https://www.westernstatesmetalroofing.com/hs-fs/hubfs/matte%20black%20corrugated%20roof%20walls.jpg?width=3600&name=matte%20black%20corrugated%20roof%20walls.jpg)
  
  **[Corrugated metal roofing prices](https://www.westernstatesmetalroofing.com/blog/corrugated-metal-roof-cost-price)** will vary based upon the size of the job, gauge of the steel, and the finish. There's no way to give you an accurate price without knowing more details. However, these are some ballpark guesstimates that should help.
  
  - **$2.50 up to $3.50 per square foot for the corrugated metal panels.**
  - Installation cost for corrugated metal roofing normally will range from $5.00 to $8.00 per square foot.
  - **Your total price including the corrugated roofing and the installation is $7.00 up to $12.00 per square foot.**
  
