  ## More Ways To Use Corrugated Metal Panels
  
  Corrugated roofs are a low cost, easy to install roofing material. At half the cost of standing seammetalroofing and a lifespan that is 2-3 times as long as an asphaltshingleroof, a corrugatedmetalroof brings exceptional value.
  
  Besides corrugated metal panels being a great choice for roofing, you can now find corrugated metal being used in popular design styles of today like farmhouse and industrial. The grooves of the corrugations on the panels add texture while the color choices are abundant, making design possibilities nearly endless.
  
  Corrugatedsteel panels or corrugated sheet can be used on a [ceiling](https://www.westernstatesmetalroofing.com/corrugated-metal-ceiling), [fence](https://www.westernstatesmetalroofing.com/blog/corrugated-metal-fencing-advantages), wainscoting, or as a [metalsiding or accent wall panel](https://www.westernstatesmetalroofing.com/corrugated-metal-siding-panel).
  
