  Roofing Panel
  
  SL175 – Snap-Lock Standing Seam Roof Panel
  
  Union's SL175 snap-lock metal roofing panel ideal for architectural and light structural applications. Secured with concealed clips for a clean look, the tall ribs snap securely together without the use of special tools to maximize uplift resistance. The snap lock metal roofing panels provide very good wind uplift resistance. Specify as an accent feature or a total roof system for schools, shopping centers, banks, hotels, offices, and a variety of other applications.
  
  Panel Coverage:  16" Coverage, 18" Coverage
  
  Rib Height:  1-3/4"
  
  Fastener:  Concealed Fastener
  
  [View Product Details](https://www.unioncorrugating.com/union-products/sl175/)
  
  [![MasterRib Specs](data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E)](https://www.unioncorrugating.com/union-products/sl150/)[![MasterRib Specs](data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E)](https://www.unioncorrugating.com/union-products/sl150/)
  
  Roofing Panel
  
  SL150 – Snap Lock Standing Seam Roof Panel
  
  Standing seam panels are suitable for roofs of traditional and contemporary homes, as well as commercial businesses, due to their outstanding durability and clean, graceful lines. SL150 is a snap-lock standing seam roof panel that installs with concealed clips for maximum wind uplift protection and weather resistance. These panels float on the roof deck, to allow expansion and contraction with temperature changes. SL150 offers a tall rib profile for a striking aesthetic.
  
  Panel Coverage:  15-7/8" Coverage
  
  Rib Height:  1-1/2"
  
  Fastener:  Concealed Fastener
  
  [View Product Details](https://www.unioncorrugating.com/union-products/sl150/)
  
  [![MasterRib Specs](data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E)](https://www.unioncorrugating.com/union-products/slimline/)[![MasterRib Specs](data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E)](https://www.unioncorrugating.com/union-products/slimline/)[![MasterRib Specs](data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E)](https://www.unioncorrugating.com/union-products/slimline/)
  
  Roofing Panel
  
  Slimline®
  
  Standing seam metal roof systems offer clean, graceful lines that are an enduring aesthetic for a wide range of architecture. Slimline panels feature 1" high ribs for a low-profile look with snap-lock seams for efficient installation. Slimline panels use an integrated fastener groove and have ribs that snap together securely without the use of clips.
  
  Panel Coverage:  16" Coverage
  
  Rib Height:  1"
  
  Fastener:  Concealed Fastener
  
