  Roof & Wall Panel
  
  PBR Panel – Purlin Bearing Leg Panel
  
  Union Corrugating's PBR metal panels are designed for industrial, commercial, and steel-frame building applications. The "R" family of metal panels has the strength to perform on roof pitches as low as 1:12 and on spans up to five feet. The IR metal roofing panels are also suitable for sidewall applications while the PBR metal roofing panel has an added purlin bearing leg to provide better support for roofing applications.
  
